 * DESCRIBEFIELD FMATY      AS MATY       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FITLD      AS ITLD       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FFCPN      AS FCPN       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FNCHD      AS NCHD       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FISSD      AS ISSD       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FDCOM      AS DCOM       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FORED      AS ORED       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FNDVD      AS NDVD       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FSCPD      AS SCPD       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FLPRU      AS LPRU       USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FLCD       AS LCD        USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FNCD       AS NCD        USING SECTYD                          :            BUG2265
 * DESCRIBEEND                                                                  :            BUG2265
